popjava.baseobject
Class ODElement

java.lang.Object
  popjava.baseobject.ODElement

public class ODElement
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents an ODElement for the object description. An ODElement is an element that has a required and a minimum value. For example, the power required for an object is set trough an ODElement. The power must have a required and a minimum value.
